00:01:06,339 --> 00:01:07,882
ABE: Ethan, no!

11
00:01:07,966 --> 00:01:09,592
These are not toys.

12
00:01:09,676 --> 00:01:12,094
-They look like toys.
-They're not.

13
00:01:12,178 --> 00:01:15,474
Go. Go. Get. Get. Go.

14
00:01:15,558 --> 00:01:17,768
How is this a toy?

15
